Overview
========

The Finatra framework uses the slf4j-api for logging. By coupling the framework to only slf4j application developers
can choose the logging implementation. This module provides a thin scala-wrapper trait (c.t.inject.Logging) over the
util-slf4j-api c.t.util.logging.Logging trait and provides a [Mapped Diagnostic Context (MDC)](https://logback.qos.ch/manual/mdc.html)
integration with slf4j and [Finagle](https://github.com/twitter/finagle) via util Locals.

See https://twitter.github.io/finatra/user-guide/logging/index.html for more information.
